        "is_projected_row_header": false,
        "xml_text_content": "To better place this item in the context of the meaning, and make it more culturally appropriate, the wording was modified to: “Problems I would experience if I had colon cancer would last a long time”. This was tested in round 2, and no further problems emerged.",
