        "is_projected_row_header": false,
        "xml_text_content": " Scale Item (Subjective norm): “Members of my immediate family think I should have colon cancer screening.” Among English language participants ( n = 3), comments indicated that the topic of colon cancer was not discussed in the family. However, for two participants, the responses were in line with their selection. Only one participant suggested having a “Not applicable” option.",
        "xml_raw_text_content": "\nScale Item (Subjective norm): “Members of my immediate family think I should have colon cancer screening.” Among English language participants (n = 3), comments indicated that the topic of colon cancer was not discussed in the family. However, for two participants, the responses were in line with their selection. Only one participant suggested having a “Not applicable” option.",
        "pdf_text_content": "Scale Item (Subjective norm): “Members of my immediate family think I should have colon cancer screening.” Among English language participants (n = 3), comments indicated that the topic of colon cancer was not discussed in the family. However, for two participants, the responses were in line with their selection. Only one participant suggested having a “Not applicable” option."
